						<a href="https://lithub.com/on-vigdis-hjorths-repetition-and-the-hidden-disenfranchisement-of-children/" title="On Vigdis Hjorth’s <em>Repetition</em> and the Hidden Disenfranchisement of Children"><img class="story-img" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Repetition-300x300.png"></a>
